I'll tell you the truth on this torrent guys. 

It's missing stuff from EPs and albums. Most of the EPs/albums/compilations on here only have one song and are missing the others.

Everything is mistagged/not tagged at all. There are MANY automatically added tags and artwork from beatport, dubjunks, and other sites.

But if you're simply looking for a mass of music from Datsik and Excision, just download this and move them into one huge album.

With a bit of research, you can use the files on this torrent to find and download other complete versions of everything on here.
